<div id="content">
<form class="form-horizontal well " id="b_logic_form">
<fieldset>
<legend>新装、去欠费、新业务等业务办理</legend>
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="alert alert-block alert-info">
  <h4 class="alert-heading"><span class="label label-warning">注意</span>业务办理</h4>
  批量号码请按每行一个号码或者以“；”进行分隔都可以。请按规定进行输入，以免出错！
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="b_s_no">批量输入号码</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <%= text_area_tag :pstn_stop,"",{:class => "span10", :size => "50x10", :id => "b_s_no",} %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_no">输入用户号码</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">K</span>
            <%= text_field :pstn_stop, "s_no", { :class => "span10", :size => "16", :id => "s_no", digits: true } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_bt">选择用户类型</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">#</span>
            <%= select(:pstn_stop, "s_bt",
                       { "普通公网用户" => "1", "语音专线" => "5", "预付费" => "7", "易套餐" => "5" },
                       { prompt: "选择用户类型" }, { class: 'span11', id: "s_bt" }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_sg_no">指定用户分组号</label>


        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">S</span>
            <%= text_field :pstn_stop, "s_sg_no", { :class => "span10", :size => "16", :id => "s_sg_no", digits: true } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_perm">选择用户权限</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">P</span>
            <%= select(:pstn_stop, "s_perm",
                       { "国内" => "1", "本地" => "2", "郊话" => "3", "国际" => "4" },
                       { prompt: "选择用户权限" }, { class: 'span11', id: "s_perm" }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_df_flag">选择欠费标志</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">$</span>
            <%= select(:pstn_stop, "s_dl_flag",
                       { "去欠费" => "1", "去欠费开机" => "2", "停机保号" => "3" },
                       { prompt: "选择欠费标志" }, { class: 'span11', id: "s_df_flag" }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_cf">选择呼叫转移</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">*</span>
            <%= select(:pstn_stop, "s_cf",
                       { "无应答转移" => "1", "无条件转移" => "2", "遇忙转移" => "3" },
                       { prompt: "选择呼叫转移" }, { class: 'span11', id: "s_cf" }) %>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_cf_no">转移到号码</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">*</span>
            <%= text_field :pstn_stop, "s_cf_no", { :class => "span10", :size => "16", :id => "s_cf_no", digits: true } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label inline" for="s_cr" name="ns">选择呼出限制</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <label class="checkbox inline">
            <%= check_box_tag :s_cr, "cr", false, { name: "ns" } %>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label" for="s_cr_no">输入呼出限制密码</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="input-prepend">
            <span class="add-on">%</span>
            <%= text_field :pstn_stop, "s_cr_no", { :class => "span10", placeholder: "默认密码为8888", :size => "16",
                                                    :id    => "s_cf_no" } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span3">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label inline" for="s_hs">选择热线服务</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <label class="checkbox inline">
            <%= check_box_tag :s_hs, "hs", false, { name: "ns" } %>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span3">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label inline" for="s_mc">选择叫醒服务</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <label class="checkbox inline">
            <%= check_box_tag :s_mc, "mc", false, { name: "ns" } %>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span3">
      <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label inline" for="s_ad">选择缩位拔号</label>

        <div class="controls">
          <label class="checkbox inline">
            <%= check_box_tag :s_ad, "ad", false, { name: "ns" } %>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="span12 offset4">
  <button id="s_b_s" class="btn btn-large btn-success span4">
    <i class="icon-ok icon-white"></i>
    数据开通
  </button>
</div>
</div>
</fieldset>
</form>
</div>
<div class="alert alert-success" id="show1">
  <span class="label label-warning" id="show2">数据提交成功</span><br/>
  后台程序正在处理中...<br/>
  由于后台数据执行较慢，请稍候再查询结果！<br/> <br/>

  <p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-success " id="sR">
      <i class="icon-chevron-left icon-white"></i> 返回</a>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-error" id="show3">
  <span class="label label-warning" id="show4">数据提交失败</span><br/>
  数据输入有错误...<br/>
  请注意各字段下标红字的字段，按规则进行修改！<br/> <br/>

  <p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger " id="dataR">
      <i class="icon-chevron-left icon-white"></i> 返回</a>
  </p>
</div>


<div class="modal hide fade" id="conModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</button>
    <h3>条件输入有错误</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <h4>
      <p>最少需要输入一个号码及一项条件才能进行操作!</p>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-large" data-dismiss="modal">关 闭</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal hide fade" id="noModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</button>
    <h3>请确认号码输入</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <h4>
      <p>批量号码和单个号码只需要输入其中任意一项，不能同时两项都输入数据，请修正后再进行操作!</p>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-large" data-dismiss="modal">关 闭</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal hide fade" id="dfModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</button>
    <h3>请确认欠费标志</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <h4>
      <p>如果你选择了欠费标志，则至少要在用户类型或分组号选填其中任意一项才可，请修正后再进行操作!</p>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-large" data-dismiss="modal">关 闭</a>
  </div>
</div>
